assets.name: Moana
assets.description: To save her island home a plucky Polynesian teen must set sail and journey into the great blue yonder. Oscar-nominated Disney animation with the voice of Dwayne Johnson. (2016)(107 mins)

assets.name: The Boss Baby
assets.description: Animated comedy about a youngster concerned that his baby brother is actually a power-hungry tycoon sent to destroy his perfect family life. With the voice of Alec Baldwin. (2017)(94 mins)

assets.name: Trolls
assets.description: A pair of fuzzy-headed trolls embark on a daring rescue mission when members of their tribe are kidnapped. Animation with the voices of Anna Kendrick and Justin Timberlake. (2016)(89 mins)

assets.name: Despicable Me 3
assets.description: Dismissed from the Anti-Villain League after botching a mission, Gru sets off to meet his long-lost twin brother. Smash-hit animated sequel. (2017)(86 mins)

assets.name: Frozen
assets.description: A plucky princess heads into the frozen forest to search for her sister, whose powers have locked the kingdom in winter. Oscar-winning Disney animation with Kristen Bell. (2013)(98 mins)

assets.name: Sing
assets.description: Family animation about a theatre-owning koala who holds a singing competition in a last-ditch bid to stay afloat. With the voices of Matthew McConaughey and John C Reilly. (2016)(103 mins)

assets.name: Baywatch
assets.description: Beloved lifeguard chief Dwayne Johnson must team up with cocky new recruit Zac Efron to take down a drug-dealing villain. Action comedy. (2017)(112 mins)

assets.name: Spider-Man: Homecoming
assets.description: Tom Holland is Peter Parker - an average teen with a web-slinging alter ego who must protect New York City from a menacing new villain. Superhero fun with Michael Keaton. (2017)(129 mins)

assets.name: Pirates Of The Caribbean: Salazar's Revenge
assets.description: ...Salazar's Revenge: Swashbuckling high-seas adventure pitting Johnny Depp's Captain Jack Sparrow against undead pirate hunter Javier Bardem. With Geoffrey Rush. (2017)(124 mins)

assets.name: Monster Family (2017)
assets.description: The first Sky Cinema Original Film sees a young family cursed by a witch and transformed into monsters. Animated comedy with the voices of Emily Watson and Jason Isaacs. (2017)(90 mins)
